comments: Kessler (UTA) raises his arm up into Embiid's (PHI) arm and initiates contact that affects his shot near the rim.
Kessler (UTA) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Alexander-Walker's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Clarkson (UTA) and Harden (PHI) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Harden (PHI) avoids making contact with Conley's (UTA) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Melton (PHI) legally contests Conley's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Alexander-Walker (UTA) brings his forearm towards Harden's (PHI) front and marginal contact occurs as Harden is passing the ball.
Alexander-Walker (UTA) is in a compromised defensive position when he makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm as he is starting his upward shooting motion.
Clarkson (UTA) advances the ball into the front court within eight seconds.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) brings his hands towards Melton (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as Horton-Tucker releases from the contact.
Harden (PHI) steps somewhat towards Clarkson (UTA) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Melton (PHI) contests Clarkson's (UTA) driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs after the release.
Milton (PHI) brings his forearm towards Kessler (UTA) and marginal contact occurs during his put back at the rim.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Alexander-Walker's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Alexander-Walker (UTA) maintains verticality and marginal contact occurs as Harden (PHI) cuts back towards the rim.
Melton (PHI) brings his hand towards Clarkson's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Melton (PHI) is retreating his arm away from Clarkson (UTA) when marginal contact occurs as Clarkson brings his left hand to the ball.
Harden (PHI) briefly grasps Alexander-Walker's (UTA) jersey as they engage during the inbound.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Horton-Tucker's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Alexander-Walker's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Embiid (PHI) places his hand momentarily on Horton-Tucker's (UTA) hip before correcting.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) is already in Thybulle's (PHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Clarkson (UTA) shuffles his feet after his gather.
Tucker (PHI) legally contests Clarkson's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
